## Research Ethics Statement

M.I.A. is designed for legitimate consciousness research purposes. Users are
responsible for:

- Following ethical guidelines in consciousness research
- Respecting privacy and confidentiality
- Using the system responsibly and not for harmful purposes
- Complying with institutional and regulatory requirements
- Acknowledging limitations and uncertainties in AI-generated research

## Data Privacy

M.I.A. processes research data locally by default. When external integrations
(MCP, web scraping) are used, users are responsible for:

- Understanding what data is being accessed
- Complying with data protection regulations (GDPR, HIPAA, etc.)
- Ensuring appropriate consent for data processing
- Implementing necessary security measures

